'''Grallia Spaceport''' was an enormous [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] located in the [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Grallia]] on [[Ralltiir/Legends|Ralltiir]]. It closed shortly after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]] by the decree of [[Lord/Legends|Lord]] [[Tion (Lord)/Legends|Tion]].

